        add("item.confluence.nazar.info3", "It is one of the ingredients of the Countercurse Mantra, which is a crafting material required to make the Ankh Charm, which can be further crafted into the Ankh Shield.");
        add("item.confluence.obsidian_rose.info", "The Obsidian Rose is that reduces the base damage taken from lava from 80 to 35 and halves the duration of the On Fire! debuff inflicted by it from 7 / 14 / 17.5 seconds to 3.5 / 7 / 8.75 seconds.");
